{"tid":539814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「最佳女友」有一種女朋友叫唐詩詠","createTime":"2018-01-25T01:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T06:06:11.000Z","uid":37501,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1614b9a7dd4be6a953e8d227771563152a4d3cd7","tid":539814,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"「做女人的，總會遇過錯的人，錯過後又會希望找到對的人共渡餘生。是啊我曾將痴心寄託在浪子身上，別人笑我傻，明知他不會專一也痴痴地等。「Amigo呢啲playboy點會肯同你結婚呀？」但旁人也看到的，我當然也看在眼內。可是，是自己喜歡的，就算難受，就算生氣也要承受。<br />\n<br />\n但之後，遇到了Tony，被他傻氣的笑容拯救了，我以為我終於可以安心，不用在每次看到另一半和其他女人上了雜誌封面後，都要徹夜難眠了。可是，和Tony一起了，我還是聽到人說「Tony同翠如真係好襯呀，佢哋應該一齊啦。」仿佛我是第三者，介入了一對璧人之間的戀情。<br />\n<br />\n我不蠢，每段感情中的瑕疵我都看到，翠如跟Tony說不如結婚吧，Tony那甜笑，我看在眼內，我們結婚吧這五個字，不應該由我的好朋友對我的男朋友說吧；翠如跟Tony說一世是好朋友，Tony的苦笑，我也看在眼內，得不到翠如有那麼苦嗎？紅地毯上，你們說翠如Tony像是天作之合，Tony一臉幸福，但給他幸福的，應該是我吧，我才是他的女朋友啊。<br />\n<br />\n翠如說，跟Tony只是好朋友，大家已有另一半。但大家想看到的，還是Tony跟翠如大團圓結局吧。可是，我就不值得有大團圓結局嗎，我才是Tony的女朋友啊。」"},{"pid":"73d9c15b225abbe228306023527a7878ae1c9317","tid":539814,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c091bc4f66b99ca1c313860f1a1679a692b78b1c","tid":539814,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"負評不多說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ba6be5ad862b5ca0bbfb48aa272c208868a6f1","tid":539814,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c091bc4f66b99ca1c313860f1a1679a692b78b1c","tid":539814,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"負評不多說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41037daa8ca488bda31774080c23276dfadce1a","tid":539814,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>負評不多說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n篇嘢真係糖寫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61336041553e2b3f8e4e5b58817147bc76827b5c","tid":539814,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"篇野似樓主寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}